data.description: Beautiful and spacious home at the end of a cul-de-sac in the City of North Pole.  Only 5 years old, this home boasts almost 1,900 square feet and was 5 star+ when built. It has triple pane vinyl windows, radiant floor heat, 9 foot ceilings and a high end, efficient Buderus boiler.  The master suite has 2 sinks and a nice walk-in closet.  Enjoy the convenience of city utilities and being located close to schools and shopping.  Short 15 min drive to Eielson AFB and only a 20 min drive to Fairbanks.
